BronzemanItems		Complete Individual item list
BrzonemanUnlocks	Unlocks that aren't items like prayers, areas, spellbooks
BronzemanItemSets	Anything that unlocks multiple items per unlock
BronzemanPvPTasks	PvP tasks
BronzemanPvMTasks	PvM tasks

